summary:
Miles: Peter! Why did you travel through the multiverse again? Is it an emergency!? Are we going to die!?
Peter: No. Much more...
body:
Miles: Peter! Why did you travel through the multiverse again? Is it an emergency!? Are we going to die!?

Peter: No. Much more important…*Pulls a picture of a red haired baby girl out of his jacket* MJ and I just had a baby! Isn’t she adorable? She’s named May but we gave her the Mayday as a nickname and she is the cutest and most precious thing in the entire world!

Miles: You risked making the multiverse collapse…because you wanted to show me baby pictures!?

Peter: I also showed Gwen, Peni, Noir, Miguel and Ham.

summary: I had this dream I was a parallel Spidey, BECAUSE, People referenced me to Tobey Macguire from Spider-Man. First joke I made to...
body:
I had this dream I was a parallel Spidey, BECAUSE, People referenced me to Tobey Macguire from Spider-Man. First joke I made to a friend after revealing myself a Spidey.

Friend: “Dude, What’re you gonna call yourself?”

Me: *Hero pose in Black/Green* “Daddy Long Legs.”
